div.p:
(i) Movable and immovable property and any other rights such as mortgages, hypothecs, privileges, usufructs, liens, sureties or pledges;
(ii) Shares in and stock and debentures of a company and any other form ofparticipation in a company;
(iii) claims to money or to any performance under contract having a financial value but does not include claims to money arising from commercial contracts resulting from the sale of goods or services, or credits granted in relation with these commercial contracts;
